Rating: 3
Delicious and extremely easy. I would suggest adding sage and bay leaves, though, and second the suggestion about rendering out the bacon first- it can be tricky to get the bacon crisp without overcooking the shallots otherwise. I used a frozen sole instead of a halibut (which was prohibitively expensive) and it worked well.

